{"tid":1232383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想多謝今日遊行派紙花既幾位女仔","createTime":"2019-06-16T15:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:18:37.000Z","uid":68090,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d61e01734cfcd8ca0f770a7d5263e2ef45d5dfdc","tid":1232383,"uid":68090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\">我今日發夢</span><br />\n夢見我行駱克道至警察總部期間<br />\n無啦啦有位女仔搞我後面<br />\n唔係....係膊頭<br />\n我望後見到個女仔俾左朵紙花我<br />\n<br />\n睇見佢地身水身汗拎住一疊A4紙<br />\n一邊示威，一邊跟住人群，一邊摺俾路人<br />\n果一刻真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我相信有其他巴絲有收到支花<br />\n<br />\n除左多謝，我諗唔到其他野幫你地<br />\n唯一可以做既就係幫你地將花放返好原位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iEe9Cy4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiEe9Cy4.png&h=61d6143c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}